name: Baby Aptos
description: What is the project about? Baby Aptos is aimed to be a multi-network supportive token for Aptos with its bAptos reflection, low tax, a good passive income for holders,a securized smart contract that can't be changed or manipulated by the team. Baby Aptos is maintained by a team of experts in cryptocurrency that knows perfectly about marketing, project development and community management. Future utilities; Baby Aptos Swap - Dex and DEFI Baby Aptos Pay - Buy some real products with your Aptos and Baby Aptos! Baby Aptos NFT Marketplace - Buy, Trade and exchange your nfts on multiple networks Baby Aptos Merchs - Buy some Baby Aptos merchs to fund the marketing and development of the Baby Aptos Ecosystem Baby Aptos Wallet - Store your cryptos on the Baby Aptos Wallet! Bridges; Binance Smart Chain will be the first network available for the token. Baby Aptos will be bridged to the Aptos network and subsequently to all other networks which Aptos has already been bridged to it. Several presales may take place for every network available for Baby Aptos, the liquidity will be merged and the price of the token will be the same on every network, without possible arbitrage trade abuse.
